title: Heikant, Gastel
data: Heikant was a hamlet in the municipality of Cranendonck, in the Dutch province of North Brabant. It is now a part of the village of Gastel (also in the municipality of Cranendonck). 51°17′06″N 5°32′49″E﻿ / ﻿51.285°N 5.547°E﻿ / 51.285; 5.547 This North Brabant location article is a stub.
